column5: The battle was next to none. Using a 2.5 inch smoked/ purple flec  tube,I managed to bring in this WGSF.  They fight hard. Thought it was a smallie.      Good for a laugh. LOL
LOL, I had one that was pushing 12" yesterday, thought it was a 2lb bass
Had those stupid thing hit topwater at night with Cudz a few weeks ago, lol!
Ok I fixed it. Thanks. DOH.  I KNEW IT WAS 4 LETTERS.
And a great fight from what I hear!!  .Love getting the bigger ones on.
Keep that secret to yerself buddy.
WH-OAH! Beasts like that put the body, mind and equipment to the test.  They say the body and equipment may survive the experience, but the mind will never be the same. Safe fishing, my friend.
Stop me if you've heard this one.  Q:  Why don't rockbass fight?  A:  Cuz theyknow they'll be released.
